brut is a GUI multitool. Among its features are: 

- partition editor, disk editor
- group/user management
- date, time, timezone

It uses gtk3 for the GUI elements.
It uses sudo. /usr/local/etc/sudoers file handles the permissions.

If it complains about missing a machine-id, run "dbus-uuidgen --ensure".

The start command is: brut


Source code:
www.github.com/random532/brut
